  "rows": [
    {
      "$id": 1,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0010",
      "style": 0,
      "name": ""
    },
    {
      "$id": 2,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0020",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Al-san.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 3,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0030",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "[ST:wide ]―How're things going?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 4,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0040",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Terrible, of course.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 5,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0050",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "And you?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 6,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0060",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I wouldn't say terrific, but[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 7,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0070",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Not bad at all.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 8,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0080",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That's great to hear.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 9,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0090",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 10,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0100",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I've always wondered something.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 11,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0110",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Even after having its cores stolen, why could the Ares\ncontinue to operate exactly as it did before?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 12,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0120",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "It was because you were there, Al-san.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 13,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0130",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I wouldn't call it a pleasant story, though.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 14,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0140",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Looking at you, Al-san,[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 15,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0150",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I feel like I'm getting closer to answering that eternal question...\nWhere in the human body does the \"heart\" reside?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 16,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0160",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Oh[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 17,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0170",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I'm sure[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 18,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0180",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "The heart isn't something that can simply fit inside a person's body.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 19,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0190",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "It's different from the human consciousness packaged inside a [System:Ruby rt=Blue Blood ]Ｂ．Ｂ．[/System:Ruby][ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 20,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0200",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "It resides in the hearts of others, reflecting that person's way of life and thinking.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 21,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0210",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "A single human's heart exists within everyone they connect with[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 22,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0220",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That's what I think.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 23,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0230",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "So a heart cannot exist purely in isolation[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 24,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0240",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Your heart, Al-san,[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 25,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0250",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "exists inside everyone who calls you a hero.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 26,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0260",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "And my heart too[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 27,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0270",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Must exist within the hearts of everyone who took the time to know me.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 28,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0280",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That's why[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 29,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0290",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That's why[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 30,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0300",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "The heart of Lao-san, who didn't forget me until his very end...[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 31,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0310",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Will continue to live on inside me.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 32,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0320",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "If you hadn't come back, Al-san,[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 33,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0330",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I...[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 34,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0340",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Might never have realized that.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 35,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0350",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That's not true.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 36,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0360",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Lin.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 37,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0370",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "You've known it all along.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 38,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0380",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Eh?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 39,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0390",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Being able to feel someone else's heart as if it were your own[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 40,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0400",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That was more than enough.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 41,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0410",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "In the end, you became Lao's hope[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 42,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0420",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "You should be proud.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 43,
      "label": "xs32270100_MSG0430",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Be proud.[ST:wait ]"
    }
  ]
}
